title: Tell me what you think of my LoL edit C:

embed.description: (No Talon Pun intended) Thanks for watching this video, I'm very pleased with how this one turned out, I've spent a very, very long time on this one, As i took the time to start using Adobe After Effects to Coincide with Vegas Pro.

I think you did a great job. + 1 sub
